## Update the new development version

Add a new section to the `CHANGELOG.md` to track changes in the
following release, meaning that if `vX.Y.Z` was just released, then
there should be a section for `vX.(Y+1).Z` that is marked \"In
Development\". Also, change the version in the `VERSION.txt` file from
`vX.Y.Z` to `vX.(Y+1).0dev`.
